  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC447">
        <l>koṭuveṉ kiḷavi yuyarntōṉ kūṟṟē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/247/mode/1up">247</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/247/mode/1up">247</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, koṭu eṉṉuñ col uyarntōṉāṟ kūṟappaṭuñ col eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'ivaṟku ūṇ koṭu, āṭai koṭu' eṉa varum.  			(51)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

